    <h1>Health and harm reduction.</h1>
    <p class="lead">The toxic-drug crisis has hit this territory hard. In the Sudbury and Manitoulin districts, drug-poisoning deaths have run at more than three times the provincial rate, and Ontario First Nations die of opioids at many times the rate of other Ontarians. None of this is anyone's failing. Help, and the tools to save a life, are available.</p>
